{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"636","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"世界首富救地球！貝佐斯捐100億美元應對氣候變遷","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-02-18 09:53</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%B2%9D%E4%BD%90%E6%96%AF.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 528px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>亞馬遜（<span lang='EN-US'>Amazon</span>）創辦人貝佐斯（<span lang='EN-US'>Jeff Bezos</span>）。（法新社）</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕世界首富、亞馬遜（<span lang='EN-US'>Amazon</span>）執行長貝佐斯（<span lang='EN-US'>Jeff Bezos</span>）<span lang='EN-US'>17</span>日宣佈，將投入<span lang='EN-US'>100</span>億美元成立「貝佐斯地球基金」（<span lang='EN-US'>Bezos Earth Fund</span>），資助科學家、行動人士、非營利組織及其他團體，以保護環境和應對氣候變遷的衝擊。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>《路透》報導，貝佐斯在<span lang='EN-US'>Instagram</span>上表示，氣候變遷是地球面臨的最大威脅，「我希望與其他人一道努力，擴大已知的方法並探索新的方法，來對抗氣候變遷對我們共同生活的這個星球所造成的毀滅性影響」。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>貝佐斯地球基金將在今年夏天開始撥款工作，貝佐斯表示，將與大企業、小公司、各國政府、全球組織和個人合作，共同採取集體行動。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>近年來，對抗氣候變遷已成為美國富豪的共同目標，包括微軟（<span lang='EN-US'>Microsoft</span>）創辦人比爾蓋茲（<span lang='EN-US'>Bill Gates</span>）、前紐約市長彭博（<span lang='EN-US'>Michael Bloomberg</span>）、避險基金經理人思特爾（<span lang='EN-US'>Tom Steyer</span>）等，都是全球最富有的環保慈善家。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3071365</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-19","clk_count":"231"}},"__N_SSG":true}